1. rails generate controller home index welcome about contact

2. config/routes.rb
get 'home/index'
get 'home/welcome'
get 'home/about'
get 'home/contact'

3. '/'
get '/', to: 'home#index'
OR
root 'home#index'

4. get '/something/:controller/:name/:action'
/something/home/aaa/index
---解释---
something 是个前缀
访问的 controller 是 home
name 参数是 aaa
方法是 index

5. match ':controller/:action/:id', via: [:get, :post]
